Not really. If we're going to get beat down now, with horrible defensive skills, then really, we have no need for any of that stuff, because soloing will NOT be much of an option.<br>
<br>
Which means we'll need to group.<br>
<br>
Which means we'll either have a HEALER, or we won't be tanking.<br>
<br>
Which means if we're not tanking we're not getting hit.<br>
<br>
Which means our Hit Points are useless since we're not getting hit.<br>
<br>
Which means DPS is all that matters.<br>
<br>
Which means we're rogues that get beaten up like Rangers.<br>
<br>
Which means we suck.<br>
<br>
Which means Fungis aren't anymore useful to us than they are to rogues.<br>
<br>
Which means they're nice for the first 40 levels or so. Then you're stuck with a mid-40s toon that has to find a group to get any kind of XP.<br>
